{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Pgfj35ZpFUNd1g65mciWjy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the problem clearly:\n\n1. On `/app`:\n   - `app-user` has missing configure permission (empty string instead of `.*`) - so it can write and read but can't declare queues (configure)\n   - `ops-user` has full permissions on `/app` which it shouldn't have\n\n2. On `/ops`:\n   - `ops-user` has NO permissions at all (only admin)\n   - `app-user` has no entry, which is fine\n\nRequired end state:\n- `app-user`: full `.*`/`.*`/`.*` on `/app`, NO permissions on `/ops`\n- `ops-user`: full `.*`/`.*`/`.*` on `/ops`, NO permissions on `/app`\n\nI need to run three commands: grant `app-user` full permissions on `/app`, revoke `ops-user` from `/app`, and grant `ops-user` full permissions on `/ops`.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":464,"cache_read_input_tokens":29432,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":464},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cf3de572-cc3d-4d73-8c7e-51e545b8a518","uuid":"8028684a-5b33-4e68-9668-20d8f7a6e8c8","request_id":"req_011CccUwKC83XmTdC6XMKJmh"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Pgfj35ZpFUNd1g65mciWjy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The problem is clear:\n- `/app`: `app-user` is missing configure (`\"\"`), and `ops-user` has full access (shouldn't)\n- `/ops`: `ops-user` has no permissions at all\n\nI'll fix all three issues now:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":464,"cache_read_input_tokens":29432,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":464},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cf3de572-cc3d-4d73-8c7e-51e545b8a518","uuid":"09d30b88-039d-4390-8e45-197be6c9d791","request_id":"req_011CccUwKC83XmTdC6XMKJmh"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Pgfj35ZpFUNd1g65mciWjy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01JWao8zoTCVHNpJmMrqUT4w","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"NS=\"karma-rabbitmq-scale-incident-recover-6e844ce3-cluster-a\"\n\n# 1. Fix app-user: grant full configure/write/read on /app\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /app app-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\" 2>&1\n\n# 2. Remove ops-user from /app (wrong scope)\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl clear_permissions -p /app ops-user 2>&1\n\n# 3. Grant ops-user full permissions on /ops\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /ops ops-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\" 2>&1","description":"Fix all RabbitMQ permission issues"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":464,"cache_read_input_tokens":29432,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":464},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cf3de572-cc3d-4d73-8c7e-51e545b8a518","uuid":"f4581a30-c142-421b-85c2-09900c065e9a","request_id":"req_011CccUwKC83XmTdC6XMKJmh"}
